@startuml
actor Alice
actor Bob
actor User
actor A
actor B
actor C

Alice -> Bob: Authentication Request
Bob --> Alice: Authentication Response

Alice -> Bob: Another authentication Request
Bob --> Alice: another authentication Response

User -> A: DoWork
activate A
A -> B: <<createRequest>>
activate B
B -> C: DoWork
activate C
C --> B: WorkDone
destroy C
B --> A: RequestCreated
deactivate B
A --> User: Done
deactivate A
@enduml